cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper is primarily focused on face recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The paper also discusses the use of convolutional neural networks (cs.LG) and proposes a novel method for synthesizing facial appearance variations (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper evaluates its approach on benchmark datasets (cs.MM) and discusses the impact of training and testing with synthesized images (cs.IR).
